name: SUGAR BUSH
description: In 2013, Charles Hoskinson tried to meme a squirrel named $SUGAR for Bitcoin Sugar Bush Squirrel is an International Superstar and the most photographed squirrel in the world. Kelly Foxton, Sugar Bush's mother had big plans to ensure Sugar Bush Squirrel would live forever. Her dreams are coming to fruition. The squirrel has piqued the interest of many new and old users on Cardano, who can't seem to get enough of this cute, inspiring creature!
